    "body": "It looks like you're trying to import from an NPM package from outside your project directory.  To do that, you shouldn't be using a file path, but should rather use Truffle's builtin ability to import from installed NPM packages.  I.e., the thing to do here would be\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\nimport \"@openzeppelin/contracts-upgradeable/proxy/utils/Initializable.sol\";\r\n```\r\n\r\nHope that's helpful!",
